ant coach &<br />director of player development)\n* [[Willie Green]] (player development)\n| otherlegend = '''(GL)''' On [[NBA G League#Player allocations|assignment]] to G League affiliate\n| otherlegend2 = '''(TW)''' Two-way affiliate player\n| roster_url = http://www.nba.com/warriors/roster/\n| transaction_url = https://stats.nba.com/transactions/\n}}\n\n==Player statistics==\n{{NBA roster statistics legend}}\n;Golden State Warriors\n{{NBA roster statistics start|team=Golden State Warriors}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Stephen|Curry}}\n| 6 || 6 || '''41.7''' || .414 || .343 || .947 || 5.2 || 6.0 || 1.5 || 0.2 || '''30.5'''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Klay|Thompson}}\n| 5 || 5 || 37.6 || .541 || .585 || .875 || 4.8 || 2.4 || 0.8 || 0.0 || 26.0\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Draymond|Green}}\n| 6 || 6 || 41.2 || .433 || .263 || .857 || '''10.8''' || '''9.3''' || '''1.7''' || 1.0 || 12.5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Kevin|Durant}}\n| 1 || 1 || 12.0 || .600 || '''1.000''' || '''1.000''' || 2.0 || 0.0 || 0.0 || 1.0 || 11.0\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Andre|Iguodala}}\n| 6 || 6 || 31.4 || .431 || .308 || .333 || 4.5 || 4.0 || 1.0 || '''1.5''' || 9.2\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|DeMarcus|Cousins}}\n| 6 || 3 || 18.0 || .425 || .222 || .609 || 4.7 || 2.3 || 0.7 || 1.0 || 8.3\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Kevon|Looney}}\n| 5 || 1 || 20.8 || .583 || .000 || .250 || 3.2 || 1.2 || 0.4 || 0.2 || 5.8\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Quinn|Cook}}\n| 6 || 0 || 14.7|| .379 || .313 || '''1.000''' || 0.8 || 0.8 || 0.2 || 0.2 || 4.8\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Shaun|Livingston}}\n| 6 || 1 || 16.3 || .417 || .000 || '''1.000''' || 1.5 || 1.5 || 0.7 || 0.2 || 4.7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{sortname|Jo